	</textbody>
	</text>
	<text xstart="15" ystart="79" xend="320" yend="531" layer="3" starttime="0" font="Calibri" fontcolour="#000000" fontsize="16"><textbody italic="true" bold="false" underlined="false"><textstring>1) Define Character Concept \n2) Choose Background \n3) Choose Faction \n4 ) Spend Free Points \n   a) 105 aptitude points \n   b) 1 Moxie \n   c) 5,000 credits \n   d) 50 Rep \n   e) Native tongue \n5) Spend Customisation Points \n   a) 1,000 CP to spend \n   b) Active skill minimum: 400 CP \n   c) Knowledge skill minimum: 300 CP \n   d) Choose starting Morph \n   e) Choose Traits \n6) Purchase Gear \n7) Choose Motivation \n8) Calculate Remaining Stats \n9) Detail the Character</textstring>
	</textbody>
	</text>
