	<textbody italic="true" bold="false" underlined="false"><textstring>+20 to two skills of your choice, -10 starting Rep\n</textstring>
	</textbody>
	<textbody italic="false" bold="true" underlined="false"><textstring>Lost:</textstring>
	</textbody>
	<textbody italic="true" bold="false" underlined="false"><textstring>+20 to two Knowledge skills of your choice, Psi trait (Level 1),\n Mental Disorder (choose two, this includes the one from Psi) trait,\n Social Stigma (Lost) trait, must start with Futura morph\n</textstring>
