	<textbody italic="true" bold="false" underlined="false"><textstring>+10 Pilot: Groundcraft skill, +10 to one Technical, Academic:\n {Field}, or Profession: {Field} skill of your choice, +20 Networking:\n Hypercorps skill\n</textstring>
